<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>상태 prop 메소드</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/public_blue.css">
<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/J.png"/>
<script src="../js/jquery-3.6.0.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script>
$(function(){
	chk = $('#checkTest').prop('checked');
	opt = $('#selTest option').eq(2).prop('selected');
	txt = $('#txtTest').prop('readonly');
	but = $('#runBtn').prop('disabled');
		
	console.log(chk, opt, txt, but);

	$('#btn1').on('click', function(){
		/*
		if(chk == true) {
			$('#checkTest').prop('checked', false);
		}else if(chk == false){
			$('#checkTest').prop('checked', true);
		}
		*/
		
	$('#checkTest').prop('checked', !$('#checkTest').prop('checked'));
	$('#selTest option').eq(2).prop('selected', !$('#selTest option').eq(2).prop('selected'));
	$('#txtTest').prop('readonly', !$('#txtTest').prop('readonly'));
	$('#runBtn').prop('disabled', !$('#runBtn').prop('disabled'));
	})
})
</script>
</head>
<body>

<pre>
확인 버튼을 누를 때마다 현재 상태값 얻어온다.
</pre>

<input type="button" value = "확인" id="btn1">
<br><br>
<div id = "d1">
	<form>
	체크박스(라디오버튼) : <input type="checkbox" id="checkTest" checked><br><br>

	리스트박스(select객체) : 
	<select id="selTest">
		<option value="1">하나</option>
		<option value="2">둘</option>
		<option value="3" selected >셋</option>
		<option value="4">넷</option>
	</select><br><br>

	text객체 (read only) : <input readonly type="text" value="가나다" id="txtTest"><br><br>

	button객체(disabled) : <input type="button" value="실행" id="runBtn" onclick="alert('Hello~~')">
</form>
</div>

</body>
</html>
